Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 8
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Two brothers harmed in a ritual that was half magic/half science seek the legendary Philosopher’s Stone to make things right. But others seek the weapon of alchemy for their own nefarious means.
Title: FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST, VOL. 21
Author: Hiromu Arakawa

Description: Naruto’s friends are threatened, the mysteries of Pain deepen and Naruto must fight to protect his village.
Title: NARUTO 46
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Who knew having wings would be such a problem? Max and her gang travel to New York in search of answers about their past.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 2
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Tsukune Aono’s new school is filled with vampires and werewolves. How is a human teenager to survive?
Title: ROSARIO VAMPIRE, VOL. 10
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work – as a boy – for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 13
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy. How will she survive the pursuit of demons who want the power in her blood?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 2
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 3
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, takes part in the Festival of Ostia, which includes a martial arts tournament. Will a team of bounty hunters ruin the plans for the day?
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 24
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: The detective known as L is scheduled to die in 23 days. That leaves him with 22 days to stop a terrorist group from unleashing a virus upon the world.
Title: DEATH NOTE: L, CHANGE THE WORLD
Author: M
